<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>93</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Hukdampa mu kimah leng,
 Ka kawmah Thu a gen zing hi;
 Amah ken ka tel apat in,
 Lalpa pakun A aw ka he'i.

[V2]
 A aw ka he'i, Hukdampa Aw!
 Aw ka lunggil a sukipak;
 Ka kawma Thu a gen chengin,
 Lalpa pakun A aw ka he'i.

[V3]
 2. A mel mu thei kimah lengle,
 Huihpi lakah A aw ka he'i;
 Tui kinawk haidi'n thu A pie'i,
 Ni hung langin muonna a um.

[V4]
 3. Ka kawmah thudik A gen hi,
 Muh phakloh, chawlhna nawpna thu;
 Muonna hehpihna thu ei hilh,
 Chunglam In nuom thu ei hilh hi.</lyrics>
<title>I KNOW HIS VOICE</title>
</song>